OL,3,CStrictly dancer Giovanni Pernice
OL,4,Cdenies claims of 'threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,FGiovanni Pernice said allegations
OL,8,Fabout his teaching methods are "simply
OL,9,Ffalse" after it was confirmed he will
OL,10,Fnot be taking part in the upcoming
OL,11,Fseason of Strictly Come Dancing.
OL,13,FThe Italian dancer has been part of
OL,14,Fthe celebrity dance competition since
OL,15,F2015, but was not included in the
OL,16,FBBC's 2024 line-up, following reports
OL,17,Fhe would not compete.
