OL,3,CStrictly dancer Giovanni Pernice
OL,4,Cdenies claims of 'threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,FIn a statement posted to Instagram on
OL,8,FSunday morning, Mr Pernice said he is
OL,9,F"co-operating fully" with an ongoing
OL,10,Finvestigation by the BBC and that he
OL,11,Fis looking forward to "clearing my
OL,12,Fname and establishing the truth".
OL,14,F"To my fans and followers, every week,
OL,15,Fthere are totally untrue stories about
OL,16,Fme in the media," the statement read.
OL,18,F"As you know, I have always rejected
OL,19,Fany suggestion of abusive or
OL,20,Fthreatening behaviour. The latest
OL,21,Faccusations are simply false.
