OL,3,CStrictly dancer Giovanni Pernice
OL,4,Cdenies claims of 'threatening
OL,5,Cbehaviour'
OL,7,F"I am so happy to be back on tour.
OL,8,FThank you all for your continued
OL,9,Fsupport - your messages and love mean
OL,10,Fso very much to me. I will hopefully
OL,11,Fsee many of you very soon and I look
OL,12,Fforward to clearing my name. With
OL,13,Flove, Giovanni."
OL,15,FMr Pernice had previously denied any
OL,16,Fallegations in a statement in May.
OL,18,FThe Sun newspaper first reported
OL,19,Fsuggestions that an investigation was
OL,20,Funderway, claiming that Mr Pernice had
OL,21,Fquit the show.
