OL,7,FA legal firm acting on behalf of the
OL,8,Fcomplainants said the BBC is currently
OL,9,F"evidence-gathering", but the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster has not confirmed whether
OL,11,Fany inquiry had begun.
OL,13,FMr Pernice is currently on tour with
OL,14,Ffellow professional dancer Anton Du
OL,15,FBeke, with whom he also hosted a
OL,16,Ftravel show.
OL,18,FIn 2021, Mr Pernice lifted the
OL,19,Fglitterball trophy with EastEnders
OL,20,Fstar and first deaf contestant Rose
OL,21,FAyling-Ellis.
